data.description: Welcome to this 4 bed, 2 bath home in the heart of Pueblo West! As you enter through the front door, a large living room greets you with gorgeous laminate floors and lots of natural light. Continue in to the kitchen and dining with tile floors, gas stove, and loads of cabinet and counter space. Adjacent the kitchen is the master suite, large enough for a king size bed. Plus a walk in closet with an attached bath! Just down the hall, you'll find 3 additional bedrooms and a guest bathroom. This home also has an unfinished basement with room to grow. Sitting on an acre of land, with a 2 car garage, this home is a must see!
